<h1>sails.config.http</h1>
<p>Configuration for your app's underlying HTTP server.  These properties are conventionally specified in the <a href="http://sailsjs.jp/documentation/anatomy/myApp/config/http.js.html"><code>config/http.js</code></a> configuration file.</p>
