<td style="text-align: center;">((object))</td>
<td>See <a href="http://sailsjs.jp/documentation/concepts/Middleware?q=conventional-defaults">conventional defaults for HTTP middleware</a></td>
<td>A configuration object of all HTTP middleware functions your app will run on every incoming HTTP request.  All <a href="https://github.com/expressjs/">Express</a> or Connect middleware is supported.<br/><a href="https://gist.github.com/mikermcneil/9cbd68c95839da480e97">Example</a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code>middleware.order</code></td>
