<td>See <a href="https://github.com/balderdashy/sails/blob/master/lib/hooks/http/index.js#l51-66">conventional defaults for HTTP middleware order</a></td>
<td>The order in which middleware should be run for HTTP request (the Sails router, which runs the appropriate explicit routes, policies, controllers, etc. from your app is invoked by the &quot;router&quot; middleware).</td>
</tr>
